limb darkening can be fitted either independently ("uncoupled") for each
filter or combined ("coupled") using prior conditioning from the PHOENIX
stellar atmosphere models. For this TransitFit uses the Limb Darkening
Toolkit (LDTk) together with filter profiles, including user-supplied
filter profiles. We demonstrate the application of TransitFit in three
different contexts. First, we model SPEARNET broadband optical data of
