the residuals is about five times lower than wavelengths assigned using
polynomial fits to individual exposures. Radial-velocity measurements of
HD 34411 showed a reduction in RMS scatter over a 10-month time baseline
from \$1.17\$ to \$1.05{\textbackslash}, m{\textbackslash},s{\textasciicircum}\{-1\}\$.},
